| 8 | **`family_tangent_signature_norm`** (REPLACED) | float (L2 norm) | lifted_singularity_v4_audit `family_tangent` | lifted-singularity fixtures only |
| 9 | **`pair_jacobian_log10_spread`** (REPLACED) | float (log10(max_sv/min_sv)) | lifted_singularity_v4_audit `constraint_jacobian_svals` | lifted-singularity fixtures only |
